<s> I beleive the Server Location Method is a better choice because: 1. DHCP doesnt have a cross platform interface to its configuration option.  </s>
<s> By using DNS, or even the raw SVRLOC multicast protocol, its still a consistent and relatively easy implementation.  </s>
<s> 2. DHCP is a one time configuration retreival, the proxy config can change dynamically, and DNS allows a mechanism to do that.  </s>
