<s> What I meant to say is that even though "system management of HTTP clients" doesn't appear in our charter, and isn't directly related to "development of the HTTP protocol", I believe that discussion of this topic is "in scope" for HTTP-WG, at least to the extent that we decide how to deal with the issue or delegate it to some other subgroup.  </s>
